+ *
+ *  - KSMBD_EVENT_LOGOUT_REQUEST(ksmbd_logout_request)
+ *    This event is to send logout request to user IPC daemon.
+ *
+ *  - KSMBD_EVENT_RPC_REQUEST/RESPONSE(ksmbd_rpc_command)
